query:
UPDATE sessions
            SET scenario_id = $2,
                scenario_discipline = $3,
                status = $4,
                started_at = $5,
                ended_at = $6,
                last_activity_at = $7,
                user_name = $8,
                evaluation_requested = $9,
                progress_flags = $10,
                mission_status = $11
            WHERE id = $1
